==Bosnian==
===Idiom===
'''ravno do Kosova'''
#literally: ''flat to Kosovo'', ''equal to Kosovo''
#not being afflicted or concerned
#: ''Rješio sam problem i sada mi je sve '''ravno do Kosova''''' (I solved a problem and I am not concerned anymore)
